<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٧٨ ... سُورَةُ النَّبَأِ ... آياتها ٤٠ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَمَّ}</span> ... عَنْ أَيِّ شَيْءٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{النَّبَإِ الْعَظِيمِ}</span> ... الخَبَرِ العَظِيمِ؛ وَهُوَ القُرْآنُ الَّذِي فِيهِ خَبَرُ البَعْثِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِهَادًا}</span> ... مُمَهَّدَةً كَالفِرَاشِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَوْتَادًا}</span> ... تُثَبِّتُ الأَرْضَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَزْوَاجًا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَصْنَافًا:</span> ذُكُورًا وَإِنَاثًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُبَاتًا}</span> ... رَاحَةً لِأَبْدَانِكُمْ، وَقَطْعًا لأَعْمَالِكُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِبَاسًا}</span> ... سَاتِرًا لَكُمْ بِظُلْمَتِهِ؛ كَاللِّبَاسِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَعَاشًا}</span> ... تُحَصِّلُونَ فِيهِ مَا تَعِيشُونَ بِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سِرَاجًا وَهَّاجًا}</span> ... مِصْبَاحًا وَقَّادًا، مُضِيئًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُعْصِرَاتِ}</span> ... السُّحُبِ المُمْطِرَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ثَجَّاجًا}</span> ... مُنْصَبًّا بِكَثْرَةٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَجَنَّاتٍ أَلْفَافًا}</span> ... بَسَاتِينَ مُلْتَفَّةً أَشْجَارُهَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِيقَاتًا}</span> ... وَقْتًا، وَمِيعَادًا لِلفَصْلِ بَيْنَ الخَلْقِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الصُّورِ}</span> ... القَرْنِ الَّذِي يَنْفُخُ فِيهِ إِسْرَافِيلُ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَبْوَابًا}</span> ... ذَاتَ أَبْوَابٍ كَثِيرَةٍ؛ لِنُزُولِ المَلَائِكَةِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسُيِّرَتِ}</span> ... نُسِفَتْ بَعْدَ ثُبُوتِهَا.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>